Usage: getModuleView [-help] [-topReadOnly ] [{-hinst <string> | -partition <string>}] [-quiet ]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-hinst <string>         # List of partition hinsts (string, optional)
-partition <string>     # List of partitions (string, optional)
-quiet                  # Suppress printing message (bool, optional)
-topReadOnly            # Is top level readOnly (bool, optional)